ent-RightHarmArm0492 = malicious right arm
    .desc = A dark steel arm. When replacing the right arm surgically, the patient gains the ability to deliver painful strikes to enemies with it.
    .suffix = SCP-049-2
ent-LeftTubeArm0492 = tubular left arm
    .desc = An elongated copper tube. When replacing the left arm surgically, the patient gains the ability to shoot their bodily waste through the tube.
    .suffix = SCP-049-2
ent-LeftSpringLeg0492 = springy left leg
    .desc = A large silver spring. When replacing the left leg surgically, the patient begins to move faster.
    .suffix = SCP-049-2
ent-OrganFlashEyes0492 = tube eyes
    .desc = Two flexible tubes with bulbs at the ends. When replacing the eyes surgically, the patient stops getting blinded by flashes.
    .suffix = SCP-049-2
ent-OrganTubeLungs0492 = pump lungs
    .desc = A pump made of fairly hard black rubber. When replacing the lungs surgically, the patient avoids falls and stops slipping.
    .suffix = SCP-049-2
ent-OrganLightingRodLiver0492 = lightning rod liver
    .desc = A compact copper part of a lightning rod. When replacing the liver surgically, the patient cannot be shocked by electric current.
    .suffix = SCP-049-2
